{{Youmay|the device|the [[Luma|tooka]]}}
A '''luma''' was a portable industrial [[Glowrod/Legends|glowrod]], commonly used in mining and construction operations. 

In [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] each used a luma illuminate their path through a [[coway shaft]] on [[Mimban/Legends|Mimban]], though they quickly turned their devices off after realizing the tunnel was naturally lit by [[Bioluminescence/Legends|bioluminescent]] [[Lichen/Legends|lichen]].<ref name="Splinter of the Mind's Eye">''[[Splinter of the Mind's Eye]]''</ref> Later, in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], Leia carried a pocket luma when [[Gender/Legends|she]] rescued Luke and [[Dev Sibwarra]] from the [[Ssi-ruuvi Imperium|Ssi-ruuvi]] [[Shree-class battle cruiser]] [[Sibwarra|''Shriwirr'']].<ref name="The Truce at Bakura">''[[The Truce at Bakura]]''</ref>

